dc_description_s: This data represents public land survey system (PLSS) corners for Outagamie County, Wisconsin in 2019. [Outagamie County related Public Land Survey System information. This is a feature class representing the section corners within Outagamie County. These points were established previously and eventually all were reset by Outagamie County.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: http://data-ocgis.opendata.arcgis.com/
